    <item>
      <title>Introduction</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/changelog/homeassistant/introduction/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/changelog/homeassistant/introduction/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Started working on a homeassistant dashboard on a raspberry pi 5. I chose HA docker over HAOS because I wanted to be able to use the raspberry pi both for running homeassistant, and acting as a display for the actual dashboard.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The dashboard is starting to look nice, however I got a lot of stabiliy issues between diffrent docker containers, at this point I might just use a second Pi and start running HAOS.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
